Name: Voyager2
Description: The Voyager1 class is the container for Voyager 2 mission-specific metadata elements.

Name: mission_phase_name
Description: The mission_phase_name attribute provides the mission-defined name of a mission phase.

Name: Earth-Jupiter Cruise
Description: Voyager 2 Cruise between Earth and Jupiter: 1997-08-20 to 1979-04-25

Name: Interstellar Mission
Description: Voyager 2 Interstellar Cruise: 1989-10-02 to End of Mission

Name: Jupiter-Saturn Cruise
Description: Voyager 2 Cruise between Jupiter and Saturn: 1979-08-05 to 1981-06-05

Name: Saturn-Uranus Cruise
Description: Voyager 2 Cruise between Saturn and Uranus: 1981-09-25 to 1985-11-04

Name: Uranus-Neptune Cruise
Description: Voyager 2 Cruise between Uranus and Neptune: 1986-02-25 to 1989-06-05

Name: spacecraft_clock_start_count
Description: The spacecraft_clock_start_count attribute provides the value of the spacecraft clock at the beginning of a time period of interest.

Name: spacecraft_clock_stop_count
Description: The spacecraft_clock_stop_count attribute provides the value of the spacecraft clock at the end of a time period of interest.
